OL,3,CClean power by 2030 target 'extremely
OL,4,Cambitious', MPs warn
OL,6,FThe UK Government's target for the
OL,7,Fcountry to be fuelled by clean power
OL,8,Fby 2030 is "extremely ambitious", a
OL,9,Fcommittee of MPs has warned.
OL,11,FThe Scottish Affairs Committee also
OL,12,Fsaid local communities should receive
OL,13,Flarger benefits if renewable power
OL,14,Fprojects are sited in their area,
OL,15,Fsuggesting the Government should at
OL,16,Fleast double its proposed level of
OL,17,Fcommunity payments.
OL,26,@pD@LOUpD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
