FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779343523
OL,3,CClean power by 2030 target 'extremely
OL,4,Cambitious', MPs warn
OL,6,FIt also said there would be a "fairer
OL,7,Fsystem for consumers across Great
OL,8,FBritain, including in Scotland" if
OL,9,Fstanding charges for electricity were
OL,10,Fmade the same across the country.
OL,12,FMPs noted that as it stands, Scotland
OL,13,Fhas "higher-than-average standing
OL,14,Fcharges", with the charges in London
OL,15,Fsaid to be 31% cheaper than they are
OL,16,Fnorth of the border.
OL,18,FThey made the calls in a report
OL,19,Fexamining the UK Government's Clean
OL,20,FPower 2030 (CP30) plan.
OL,26,@nD@_OUpD@_O]uD@EOUvD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779343523
OL,3,CClean power by 2030 target 'extremely
OL,4,Cambitious', MPs warn
OL,6,FThe drive to fuel the UK by low-carbon
OL,7,Fenergy is one of five national
OL,8,Fmissions set out by Prime Minister Sir
OL,9,FKeir Starmer, but MPs on the committee
OL,10,Fwarned "the clean power by 2030 target
OL,11,Fis extremely ambitious".
OL,13,FMPs added they "would suggest the
OL,14,FGovernment must use all the levers it
OL,15,Fpossesses if it is to achieve it".
OL,17,FAs part of this, they suggested GB
OL,18,FEnergy ` the publicly-owned energy
OL,19,Fcompany set up by the Government `
OL,20,Fdoes more.
OL,26,@rD@HOUsD@WO]uD@POUwD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779343523
OL,3,CClean power by 2030 target 'extremely
OL,4,Cambitious', MPs warn
OL,6,FGB Energy was "billed as a key
OL,7,Fvehicle" in meeting the 2030 clean
OL,8,Fenergy target, but in the MPs said:
OL,9,F"If Great British Energy is to become
OL,10,Fthe catalyst required to accelerate
OL,11,Frenewable generation and meet CP30, it
OL,12,Fmust now move quickly beyond the
OL,13,Finitial start-up phase and scale up
OL,14,Fdelivery."
OL,26,@nD@OOUoD@HO]qD@AOUvD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779343523
OL,3,CClean power by 2030 target 'extremely
OL,4,Cambitious', MPs warn
OL,6,FNoting that Scotland has more than
OL,7,F1,000 new renewable energy projects in
OL,8,Fthe planning pipeline ` with an
OL,9,Festimated capacity of 83 gigawatts
OL,10,F(GW) ` the MPs said Scotland will be a
OL,11,F"cornerstone of the UK's clean power
OL,12,Ftransition".
OL,14,FBut they added Scots currently have
OL,15,F"higher-than-average standing charges"
OL,16,Fon their electricity bills, with this
OL,17,F"largely reflecting the higher costs
OL,18,Fof transporting power to rural areas
OL,19,Fcompared with large population
OL,20,Fcentres".
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@KO]wD@AOUwD@fO]yD@AOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779343523
OL,3,CClean power by 2030 target 'extremely
OL,4,Cambitious', MPs warn
OL,6,FThe MPs went on to note: "The burden
OL,7,Fof higher standing charges is
OL,8,Fparticularly acute for Scotland's
OL,9,Fremote and island communities, who
OL,10,Falso experience higher levels of fuel
OL,11,Fpoverty and, in many cases, are
OL,12,Fbearing the brunt of the
OL,13,Finfrastructure required to deliver UK-
OL,14,Fwide clean power ambitions.
OL,16,F"This disparity risks undermining
OL,17,Fpublic confidence in the transition
OL,18,Fand exacerbating inequalities,
OL,19,Fparticularly in the short-term, as
OL,20,Fincreased infrastructure investment
OL,21,Fpushes up bills."
OL,26,@nD@ZOUxD@AOU}D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779343523
OL,3,CClean power by 2030 target 'extremely
OL,4,Cambitious', MPs warn
OL,6,FTo make a "fairer system", the
OL,7,Fcommittee said the Government should
OL,8,F"introduce a standing charge that
OL,9,Fapplies consistently to all regions".
OL,11,FWhile ministers have already promised
OL,12,Fthat communities near renewable energy
OL,13,Fprojects will benefit, the committee
OL,14,Fsaid the payments to local areas
OL,15,Fshould be higher.
OL,17,FThe UK Government has proposed a
OL,18,Fcontribution of #5,000 per megawatt
OL,19,F(MW) of installed capacity, but the
OL,20,FMPs said payments of #10,000-#12,500
OL,21,Fper MW "seem appropriate".
OL,26,@nD@KOUnD@YO]pD@AOUqD@dO]}D@HOU}D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779343523
OL,3,CClean power by 2030 target 'extremely
OL,4,Cambitious', MPs warn
OL,6,FThey said they reached this conclusion
OL,7,Fafter hearing from Highland Council
OL,8,F"that #12,500 is a fair and
OL,9,Fproportionate level of compensation"
OL,10,Fas it "reflects the council's first-
OL,11,Fhand experience of clean energy
OL,12,Fdeployment, as well as the lived
OL,13,Fexperience of communities currently
OL,14,Fimpacted by renewables".
OL,16,FCommittee chairwoman Patricia Ferguson
OL,17,Fsaid: "Scotland will play a pivotal
OL,18,Frole in ensuring that the UK
OL,19,FGovernment achieves its ambitions for
OL,20,Fclean power.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@dO]rD@GOUvD@WO]yD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779343523
OL,3,CClean power by 2030 target 'extremely
OL,4,Cambitious', MPs warn
OL,6,F"For these missions to succeed, it's
OL,7,Fcrucial that communities `
OL,8,Fparticularly those in rural and remote
OL,9,Fareas who have been asked to host new
OL,10,Fenergy infrastructure ` feel that the
OL,11,Fenergy transition is being done with
OL,12,Fthem, not to them.
OL,14,F"We've concluded that the Government's
OL,15,Fproposed mandatory community benefits
OL,16,Fscheme doesn't go far enough.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779343523
OL,3,CClean power by 2030 target 'extremely
OL,4,Cambitious', MPs warn
OL,6,F"Communities must receive fair
OL,7,Fcompensation for shouldering the
OL,8,Fburden of the energy transition `
OL,9,Fespecially when many are already
OL,10,Fexperiencing fuel poverty.
OL,12,F"We're also calling for the UK
OL,13,FGovernment to take further action to
OL,14,Fsupport Scottish people during this
OL,15,Ftransition, by introducing fairer,
OL,16,Fmore consistent standing charges
OL,17,Facross the UK."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
