OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779343523
OL,3,CClean power by 2030 target 'extremely
OL,4,Cambitious', MPs warn
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,7,FEnergy Security and Net Zero said: "We
OL,8,Fhave always been clear that
OL,9,Fcommunities hosting clean, homegrown
OL,10,Fpower should directly benefit from it.
OL,12,F"That is why we are continuing to
OL,13,Fexplore plans for mandatory benefits
OL,14,Ffor those hosting energy
OL,15,Finfrastructure like onshore wind and
OL,16,Fsolar farms, with communities deciding
OL,17,Fwhere funds go for their own specific
OL,18,Farea."
OL,26,@oD@dOUtD@AOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
